q 0 0 10 12 rectclip
1 0 0 -1 0 12 cm q
q
0 0 10 12 re W n
% Fallback Image: x=0 y=0 w=10 h=12 res=300ppi size=6300
[ 10.08 0 0 -12 0 12 ] concat
/cairo_ascii85_file currentfile /ASCII85Decode filter def
/DeviceRGB setcolorspace
<<
